d":1024193,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T02:02:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T03:34:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/owh2z0X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fowh2z0X.jpg&h=5fb12000&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EYa0mFX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEYa0mFX.png&h=f7e96e86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t48Uq7D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft48Uq7D.jpg&h=847db109&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa44475d046e6f1dceb66c5a9d5206e7b5069df2","tid":1024193,"uid":102226,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T03:55:26.000Z","msg":"Stink bugs do not reproduce inside, therefore they invade homes from the outside. They go through a simple metamorphosis: egg, nymph, and adult. Nymphs feed throughout the summer and molt to adults in late summer. The eggs of a stink bug can be found on the underside of leaves in clumps of <strong>20-30 eggs.</strong><br />\n<br />\nThis is the time where their numbers begin to multiply exponentially, as a single female stink bug can lay up to <strong>400 eggs </strong>over the course of a summer. From May through August, those eggs hatch and the flightless, juvenile stink bugs &ndash; called nymphs &ndash; start feeding on vegetables and fruit.<br />\n<br />\n香港昆蟲學會會長饒戈指出，每年5至8月是臭屁蟲產卵的高峰期，牠們愛在深色或淺色的衣物上產卵，蟲蛋呈圓球形，每次產卵<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>通常</strong></span>會誕下<strong>14粒</strong>，排列密密麻麻<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37aa1031d1960521a0f9c4b54339971119e35174","tid":1024193,"uid":158933,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"aa44475d046e6f1dceb66