/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07cd33e8cc43bca47cb1ca27d91b8ae2db047a0b","tid":1024193,"uid":94045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T08:56:57.000Z","msg":"我記得以前小學，一到夏天成日個後樓梯周圍都係呢啲蟲，果時唔識野，跟住用腳大大力踢飛佢，佢都可以跌落地完全無事，剩係可以聽到，噠一聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}